If SSL is off, this is a finding.

Consult network administration staff to determine whether the server is protected by NSA-approved encrypting devices. If not, this a finding.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA></STIG_DATA><STIG_DATA><VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Fix_Text</VULN_ATTRIBUTE><ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Note: The following instructions use the PGDATA and PGVER environment variables. See supplementary content APPENDIX-F for instructions on configuring PGDATA and APPENDIX-H for PGVER.

